      <h1 class="text-[2rem] leading-[1.08] sm:text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-bold sm:leading-[1.05] mb-4 sm:mb-6 tracking-tight text-gray-800">
        <span data-i18n="home.hero.title">Where your best self is finally</span> <span class="text-gradient" data-i18n="home.hero.measurable">measurable</span>.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg md:text-2xl text-gray-500 mb-6 sm:mb-10 leading-relaxed font-medium px-1 sm:px-0" data-i18n="home.hero.lead">
        Join the curated community of radiant individuals. Unlock the life you deserve, pristine social harmony, and real world perks.
